{"tid":1321272,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到警察同示威者兩邊都有畀對方圍住打嘅情況， 點解有記者會幫警察擋，而唔覺有記者幫示威者擋？","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:57:16.000Z","uid":116340,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"97a9b77250145f161075551948f1170c8d0c21ba","tid":1321272,"uid":116340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/apnewssss1_c7yka_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fapnewssss1_c7yka_1200x0.png&h=74c09d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1435535666534854/posts/2381566121931799/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1435535666534854%2Fposts%2F2381566121931799%2F&d=VPbJsUOTS2%2BU35Cb01K8cC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=42eced75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1435535666534854/posts/2381566121931799/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完呢篇諗咗陣&hellip;<br />\n點解會有記者幫警察擋圍毆，而唔覺有記者幫示威者擋圍毆？<br />\n<br />\n我諗唔係立場問題，正如文中所講，有為數不少嘅記者係偏向同情示威者。<br />\n<br />\n我諗亦都唔係因為邊一方暴力啲危險啲，怕搞出人命先過去擋，因為雙方都可以好危險。<br />\n<br />\n如果喺記者角度理性啲諗，示威者圍毆警察嘅時候過去幫手擋的話，會成功做到人肉盾牌，停止圍毆情況，記者同警察都全身而退。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>記者會過去擋係因為佢地相信示威者唔會攻擊佢地。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁如果警察圍住打示威者嘅時候，記者過去幫手擋呢，個情況又會係點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0593ddc4d4400899a3b293d9808d34ee15c9b1c","tid":1321272,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"又好難咁講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26465a9c1e9611a94e6401616560df9d7708007b","tid":1321272,"uid":152147,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:30:14.000Z","msg":"你有冇見過狗癲起上黎係會唔咬人？"},{"pid":"f78d070970a2230ee7e69a60d3139437502f03eb","tid":1321272,"uid":116340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:34:58.000Z","msg":"普遍被警察認為偏幫示威者嘅記者們，竟然救警察勇猛過救示威者， 無論背後係咩原因，都叫警察情何以堪"},{"pid":"c781da2f20ee8cf0292e9101d1e68f0b23bf3315","tid":1321272,"uid":245590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"記者teabag補尾刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806cbdc8c119c55ee133acad58cccd530846f220","tid":1321272,"uid":220853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:52:09.000Z","msg":"佢肯行埋黎影住你已經係幫緊你<br />\n冇鏡頭既話我諗有人死左都冇人知"},{"pid":"729d4cddc69cc6a60ae2ff1211448b8023639922","tid":1321272,"uid":267056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"呢個好似cctvb 尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c736f9a47c8900f538efb7e6e971a9e16672586","tid":1321272,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:54:05.000Z","msg":"係，琴晚tbb報道有呢個camman段片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfbe7f679066aecbc5e427d9d7c2568379baa604","tid":1321272,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"志森與志豪今集有傾呢個topic, 幫示威者擋會俾人拉，但唔幫就係條人命黎，係好兩難。。。"},{"pid":"31a149339011640c89073d12ffc2c4e667c3df45","tid":1321272,"uid":245590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xvgj9Oy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvgj9Oy.png&h=ee036e90&s={SIZE}\" />記者：你地打夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}